snippet.title: Cercle
snippet.description:
Cercle produces unique experiences, by organizing, filming and broadcasting concerts in carefully selected locations around the world.

Our prime goal is to showcase cultural heritage and landmarks throughout the prism of electronic music and video.

Each show is different, live events happen on Mondays, and replays are released on YouTube on Thursdays/Fridays.

Make sure to subscribe in order to see the next videos: http://bit.ly/2BINQUh

And if you want to feel the Cercle experience live, subscribe to our newsletter for news about the next events! lnk.to/Cerclenewsletter

And if you want to give your dream location(s) or artist(s) for a Cercle show: https://cercle.lnk.to/letusknowyouridea
